	   <tr><td colspan=2>Not sure about the Held Item listing, but you don't have to worship a god to make the idol.&nbsp;&nbsp;You have to worship a god to imbue the gem needed to make the idol.  For example, only a Cazic Thule worshipping Shaman could imbue the Amber needed to make this idol.  And, you'd need an enchanter to make the vial of clear mana, and a rogue to make the white lead needed to make the Divine Crystalline Glaze, which is used in the firing process.  And, it trivializes over 200.  Basically, if you ever make one of these, you are one of the privileged few.  Hopefully I can be so lucky.<br><br>Sunil Grubsov<br>Iksar Necro (Level 27 Occultist)<br>Vazaelle<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
